    Enclosing class:
    HamletSpec

    public static interface HamletSpec._InsDel
    INS and DEL are unusual for HTML "in that they may serve as either block-level or inline elements (but not both)".
    cf. http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/struct/text.html#h-9.4
    cf. http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/edits.html#edits
